node.text: This is Wings of Rescue. Our sponsor, @titosvodka, will match up to $20,000 in donations sent their way through the link in our bio. Wings of Rescue flies dogs like Clyde from overcrowded shelters and disaster areas to shelters with empty kennel space where they’ll be adopted in no time. They’ve saved 8,597 pets this year already and can save way more with your help. Everyone involved gets a 14/10 from us [EDIT: initial goal of $20k hit in 45 minutes, secondary goal of $40k hit in 3 1/2 hours]

node.text:
This is Lola. Today she won first place in the “Most Gorgeous Oldie” competition. Always knew she had what it takes but it’s nice to be validated. 14/10 #SeniorPupSaturday (follow @abs_dawg_pound)

Lola has had her consultation with @JustFoodForDogs and has decided on the Chicken & White Rice diet. You can learn more about their fresh whole food movement by clicking the link in our bio (4th one down) 🤗 #partner

node.accessibility_caption: A gorgeous white lab is smiling at the camera. She is wearing a big blue ribbon that indicates she won the Most Gorgeous Oldie competition.
The same white lab is now jumping for joy in the backyard with her ribbon.
Photo by WeRateDogs® on September 03, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, dog and text that says 'BAP'.

node.text:
This is Sokka. Last Saturday night he was hit by a car. The car sped off and Sokka was left with large skin injuries requiring stitches. We’ve covered the remaining cost of his emergency care. He’s doing much better now. 13/10

This week we were sent 112 GoFundMe’s totaling $884,489 in requested funds. We sadly can’t fund them all. Please consider getting @trupanion through the link in our bio (third one down from there), so you never have to send us one. It’s best to be puppared ❤️ #partner

node.text: This is Muffin. She was rescued in the aftermath of Hurricane Ida by @laspca. They’ve been working nonstop to rescue displaced animals and provide vet care to affected communities. They desperately need donations through the link in our bio (fifth one down from there). 14/10 for all

node.text: This is Luka and Ferris. Once a week they take a hot air balloon ride to the tulip fields. Magical as h*ck. 14/10 for both (follow @ferrisdrueller)
